title: What My Life Has Really Been Like After Being on Reality TV!
itunes:title: What My Life Has Really Been Like After Being on Reality TV!
description:
In this episode, Kimberly Cobb recaps her river floating trip, vents about being ghosted, gets real about what life has really been like since being on reality tv, & more!

 

Follow for weekly episodes of the "My Lips Aren't Sealed" podcast, where I discuss dating, fashion, entertainment, travel, pop culture, and more from my life! Thanks for listening!
